definitions.text:
@đưa đà
- Say with a smooth tongue
=Đưa đà vài câu chứ chẳng thực tâm+To say a few words with a smooth tongue actually out of insincerity

@đưa đường
* verb
- to guide, to lead the way

@đưa chân
- See (somebody) off
=Đưa chân khách ra khỏi làng+To see a guest off from the gate of the village

@đưa cay
- Wash down with alcohol
=Phải có cái gì ngon ngon để đưa cay+We must have some relishes to wash down with this wine

@đưa
* verb
- to conduct; to escort; to bring; to take; to pass; to give

@đưa đón
* verb
- to meet and see off

@đưa tình
* verb
- to ogle; to make eyes (at)

@đưa tin
* verb
- to inform, to publish news
